---
type: article
title: RHINE API
source: http://www.rhine.io/
date: Jan 12, 2015 06:43 PM
---
Humans have a thorough knowledge of how concepts in the real world connect together. For example, we know that a baseball glove is more related to a baseball bat than it is to a soccer ball.

Rhine is the first intelligence engine that is able to understand how objects and concepts in the real world connect together. Our knowledge engine captures associations between topics and concepts at a human level.

Given two entities, Rhine can return an association score. The smaller the score, the more they are related.